        "# Data Wrangling and Insights: The WeRateDogs Ecosystem"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "f49a8515"
      },
      "source": [
        "> **Analyst:** Almostafa Alashrey  \n",
        "> **Tools:** Python, Pandas, Tweepy API, Requests, Seaborn\n",
        "\n",
        "## 1. Project Overview\n",
        "This project focuses on the end-to-end data pipeline for the **WeRateDogs** Twitter account. Real-world data is rarely clean; this analysis demonstrates the transition from fragmented, \"dirty\" data sources to a unified, professional-grade dataset ready for statistical modeling and visualization.\n",
        "\n",
        "### The Business Question\n",
        "How do dog \"stages\" and breeds influence social media engagement (likes/retweets), and can we predict popular content based on image classifications?"
      ]
    },
