      "source": [
        "## Assessing Data\n",
        "In this phase, I performed both visual and programmatic assessments to identify 8 quality issues and 2 structural (tidiness) issues. This "detective work" ensures the integrity of the subsequent analysis.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Note:** Key considerations during data assessment included focusing on original ratings (excluding retweets) with associated images. While the dataset contains over 5000 tweets, not all are dog ratings, and some are retweets. The assessment and cleaning process focused on addressing at least 8 quality issues and 2 tidiness issues. The unique rating system (e.g., numerators greater than denominators) was intentionally preserved as it is a characteristic of WeRateDogs. Data gathering was limited to tweets up to August 1st, 2017, due to limitations in image prediction data availability for later tweets."
      ]
    },
